Author: Domenic Franjic [aut, cre] (<franjic@uni-hohenheim.de>)
Maintainer: Domenic Franjic <franjic@uni-hohenheim.de>
Description: The package uses sparse principal components analysis and the Kalman filter
    and smoother to estimate a sparse Gaussian state-space model with mixed frequency
    data.
